flowRoot.flowPara: Evaluation was done on Movies, wehere we have a ground truth in our test set.
Movies from TMDB, which have an IMDB id.
Determining the best threshold for the
actor overlap, when a match is recognized. Tests in 5% steps. You can see, that a threshold of ~ 70 % yields the best results.
This values might be biased by the fact, that we only match those movies, where we already have an IMDB id from TMDB.
It could be, that these movies are maintained better than the ones without a IMDB id.
